textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value HWADDR ([0-9a-f:]{17})
Value INET_ADDR (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value BCAST (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value MASK (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value INET6_ADDR ([0-9a-f:]+/[0-9]+)
Value SCOPE (\S+)
Value MTU (\d+)
Value METRIC (\d+)
Value RX_PACKETS (\d+)
Value RX_ERRORS (\d+)
Value RX_DROPPED (\d+)
Value RX_OVERRUNS (\d+)
Value RX_FRAME (\d+)
Value TX_PACKETS (\d+)
Value TX_ERRORS (\d+)
Value TX_DROPPED (\d+)
Value TX_OVERRUNS (\d+)
Value TX_CARRIER (\d+)
Value COLLISIONS (\d+)
Value TXQUEUELEN (\d+)
Value RX_BYTES (\d+)
Value TX_BYTES (\d+)

Start
  ^${INTERFACE}\s+Link\s+encap:Ethernet\s+HWaddr\s+${HWADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+inet\s+addr:${INET_ADDR}\s+Bcast:${BCAST}\s+Mask:${MASK}\s*$$
  ^\s+inet6\s+addr:\s*${INET6_ADDR}\s+Scope:${SCOPE}\s*$$
  ^\s+.*\s+MTU:${MTU}\s+Metric:${METRIC}\s*$$
  ^\s+RX\s+packets:${RX_PACKETS}\s+errors:${RX_ERRORS}\s+dropped:${RX_DROPPED}\s+overruns:${RX_OVERRUNS}\s+frame:${RX_FRAME}\s*$$
  ^\s+TX\s+packets:${TX_PACKETS}\s+errors:${TX_ERRORS}\s+dropped:${TX_DROPPED}\s+overruns:${TX_OVERRUNS}\s+carrier:${TX_CARRIER}\s*$$
  ^\s+collisions:${COLLISIONS}\s+txqueuelen:${TXQUEUELEN}\s*$$
  ^\s+RX\s+bytes:${RX_BYTES}\s+\(.*\)\s+TX\s+bytes:${TX_BYTES}\s+\(.*\)\s*$$ -> Record
